  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 20px;white-space: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4255555555555556\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: top;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5e9ec0e2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLj2JukicGRGZsPvnVpm6GkVLvevjOxYWib8l6pIJhUXfOq4Bs5noY4QWgIN3CDhv5X8FNn5CQv6Psmg%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin: 15px 8px 35px;\">\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: normal;font-size: 15px;padding: 0 10px;border-left: 3.5px solid #00b0ec;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">总裁现场喊话AI点40杯奶茶，然后骑手送到了！阿里千问这次玩真的。</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin: 10px 8px 7.5px;white-space: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-align: right;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">作者 | &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"display: inline-block;width: 63px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">李水青</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 10px 8px 35px;white-space: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-align: right;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">编辑 | &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"display: inline-block;width: 63px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">心缘</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">智东西1月15日杭州报道，今日，千问App上线</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">超400项AI办事功能</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，成为</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">全球首个能完成真实生活复杂任务的AI助手</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">千问App全面接入</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">淘宝、支付宝、淘宝闪购、飞猪、高德</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">等阿里生态业务，在全球首次实现</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">点外卖、买东西、订机票</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">等AI购物功能，并向</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">所有用户</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">开放测试。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px 8px;margin-top: -10px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=96d5ba56&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLj2JukicGRGZsPvnVpm6GkVLBBg3ocviapibWAcjibaxnuphZXlgznJGS6mBjnfmS6Hl42vM78THNNOibg%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">同时，千问App“</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">任务助理</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">”开启邀测，包括移动端和网页端两个版本，覆盖</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">报表制作、查资料做报告、信息可视化、做工具网页、旅游路线规划、教育板书讲解</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">等众多典型应用场景。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px 8px;margin-top: -10px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0a579251&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLj2JukicGRGZsPvnVpm6GkVL5AGLHPrjZcmbcCH6C5ib0KPnyUBiaVq1EktrIKMPJXmPbotL3P1SkjYA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">阿里巴巴副总裁、阿里千问C端事业群总裁吴嘉提到，千问App上线两个月以来，C端月度活跃用户已突破</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">1亿</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。他说，现在这只是千问App办事的第一个版本，</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">未来大家可能只需要下载千问一个App，</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">而不像传统互联网时代，</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">需要在多个App中频繁切换。</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px 8px;margin-top: -10px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=64cca0d8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLj2JukicGRGZsPvnVpm6GkVLUKRjx07dfXzxMIHjeyRybGTvFicSDPCgnvGiaSokOm0ddLQd976h6g4w%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在发布会上，吴嘉现场演示了</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">用千问App点“第一杯奶茶”</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。他给千问App下达一句话指令：“帮我点40杯霸王茶姬的伯牙绝弦”，千问App迅速调用淘宝闪购下单，无需任何跳转即在端内完成AI支付。不久后，淘宝闪购骑手就将奶茶送达现场。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px 8px;margin-top: -10px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=391f5679&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLj2JukicGRGZsPvnVpm6GkVLJ3afDcgxQk1to5VibD7WrvKodgxqASmUjibTFrmnmM3zREg1yTCCEx3A%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">01</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">阿里吴嘉：三大底层能力突破</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">驱动千问现实“办事”能力升级</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">吴嘉称，千问App上线办事能力，这不仅是在线上数字世界帮大家办事，更是要进入物理世界，在生活环境中帮人们办事，形成AI办事的完整形态。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在数字世界，</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">AI将从副驾驶走向主驾驶</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。千问App主要依赖</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">三大能力：全模态理解、AI Coding和超长上下文工程</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">千问大模型Coding能力的大幅提升，使其能实时构建工具；全模态理解能力的突破，让千问能够看懂界面听懂声音同时读懂图文报表；最后是超长上下文的处理能力大幅提升复杂上下文的交付上限。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px 8px;margin-top: -10px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=68e0f745&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLj2JukicGRGZsPvnVpm6GkVLKZWb4Zm5WoCnObYQfbk9nnfYUnH2yiaZicFz2ZKlIlsYxIGK3HMGlTPA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">千问App“任务助理”即日起开启邀测，将在不久后全面开放。吴嘉称，千问App“任务助理”几乎可以处理数字世界的任何事务，覆盖报表制作、查资料做报告、信息可视化、做工具网页、旅游路线规划、教育板书讲解等众多典型场景。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px 8px;margin-top: -10px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6708845d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLj2JukicGRGZsPvnVpm6GkVLT7QxfiayEk8mJzEJ7sKibGMVVfZNSIibMNLM6pesbXUevWtMa4IuBFfOA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在真实生活场景，模型需要深度理解真实世界生活需求，并且具备从消费到交易的全链路能力，对此阿里提供丰富的商品和服务供给，并且具备海量的真实反馈和交易。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px 8px;margin-top: -10px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=23b8c3f1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLj2JukicGRGZsPvnVpm6GkVL0AIicrkS1Y1QAZr1ZCRFliaiaAibedkIQKwDCz9WUUAicCBM3Weh8NGbMPw%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">千问App宣布全面接入阿里生态场景，包括淘宝、支付宝、淘宝闪购、飞猪、高德、1688、盒马、优酷、大麦娱乐、阿里健康、菜鸟生态业务组，点外卖、买东西、订机票、订酒店等AI购物功能开放测试。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px 8px;margin-top: -10px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=17cd9e9c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLj2JukicGRGZsPvnVpm6GkVLTPpw89UB2IRtfbPrpMRR6Ufl71baHxE2lWKjmbFLYFaM8XWKVP5zYg%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">吴嘉称：“千问是第一个真正能帮你办事的AI，我们的独特优势在于‘Qwen最强模型’与‘阿里最丰富生态’的结合，AI办事时代才刚刚开始。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;\"